title: Emblem
content:
Emblem may refer to:

  • Ancient emblem, one of six ancient artefacts obtained as drops from revenants
  • Antique emblem, emblems obtained by killing targets in Bounty Hunter, replacing mysterious emblems
  • Archaic emblem, former mysterious emblems that were converted and eventually be removed
  • Emblem Trader, an NPC who sells mysterious emblems and runs the Bounty Hunter Shop
  • Mysterious emblem, emblems sold by the Emblem Trader
  • Mounted emblem, a piece of furniture featuring a decorative emblem
  • Unstrung emblem, an unstrung unholy symbol
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
